Package com.palomamobile.android.sdk.messageThread

At a high level the com.palomamobile.android.sdk.messageThread package of Message SDK supports thread based group chats.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMessageThreadManager
    Created by Karel Herink
    IMessageThreadService
    This interface is consumed by the Retrofit library to provide access to the message threading functionality of the Paloma Mobile Platform Sharing and Messaging Service RESTful API.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseMessageThread
    Abstract class BaseMessageThread represents common information available about a messageThread in the context of the Message SDK.
    EventMessageThreadDeleted
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once the list of messageThreads changes as a result of messageThread deletion.
    EventMessageThreadMemberAdded
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once the list of messageThread members changes as a result of messageThread member addition.
    EventMessageThreadMemberDeleted
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once the list of messageThread members changes as a result of messageThread member deletion.
    EventMessageThreadMembersReceived
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once the list of messageThread members is received.
    EventMessageThreadMessagesReceived
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once the list of messageThread messages is received on the client.
    EventMessageThreadPosted
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) when a messageThread is posted by the client.
    EventMessageThreadReceived
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) when an existing messageThread is received by the client.
    EventMessageThreadsDeleted
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once all users messageThreads are deleted.
    EventMessageThreadsReceived
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) once the list of messageThreads is received on the client.
    EventMessageThreadUpdated
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) when a messageThread is updated by the client.
    JobAddMessageThreadMember
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.addMessageThreadMember(String, long, long, String) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadMemberAdded on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobDeleteMessageThread
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.deleteMessageThread(String, long) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadDeleted on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobDeleteMessageThreadMember
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.deleteMessageThreadMember(String, long, long) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadMemberDeleted on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobDeleteMessageThreads
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.deleteMessageThreads(String, long) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadsDeleted on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobGetMessageThread
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.getMessageThread(String, long) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadReceived on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobGetMessageThreadMembers
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.getMessageThreadMembers(String, long, Map, String, String...) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadMembersReceived on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobGetMessageThreadMessages
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.getMessages(String, long, Map, String, String...) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadMessagesReceived on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobGetMessageThreads
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.getMessageThreads(String, long, Map, String, String...) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadsReceived on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobPostMessageThread
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.postMessageThread(String, NewMessageThread) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadPosted on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobPostMessageThreadMessage
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.postMessage(String, long, MessageSent) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageSentPosted on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
    JobUpdateMessageThread
    Convenience wrapper around IMessageThreadService.updateMessageThread(String, long, MessageThreadUpdate) Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMessageThreadUpdated on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
